OL,5, A film writer appointed chancellor of a
OL,6, university in his hometown says he     
OL,7, wants to "give something back" to the  
OL,8, place that changed his life.           
OL,10,FSarfraz Manzoor moved to Luton in 1964 
OL,11,Fand wrote the memoir Greetings from    
OL,12,FBury Park, which was made into the     
OL,13,Fmovie Blinded by the Light.            
OL,15,FHe is now the chancellor of the        
OL,16,FLuton-based University of Bedfordshire.
OL,18,FHe said the town was often seen in a   
OL,19,Fnegative way, but "it doesn't have to  
OL,20,Fbe like that".                         
